Course Proposal Listing

Note: This document currently contains the list of routed pages in the project where a “course/proposal”-related page exists. If you meant actual course objects/data from a specific module (e.g., `src/data/*` or `src/content/*`), point me to that file/module name and I will regenerate this doc with the exact course titles and their full content.

